<collectingCountry box="[225,273,1571,1592]" name="India" pageId="13" pageNumber="452">Hind</collectingCountry>
trochanter without such patch. Aedeagal box elongated (
<figureCitation box="[836,916,1571,1592]" captionStart="FIGURE 10" captionStartId="12.[151,250,1400,1422]" captionTargetBox="[182,1407,197,1366]" captionTargetId="figure@12.[170,1417,193,1379]" captionTargetPageId="12" captionText="FIGURE 10. Aedeagal box of Merodon rasicus sp. n. A – L. ventral view; A – F. lateral view; G – L. Turkey, Hakkari: A, G. Iran, Fars Darab: B, H. Greece, Kavala: C, I. Turkey, Mardin: D, J. Serbia, Kopaonik: E, K. “ Poland ”: F, L." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/245537/files/figure.png" pageId="13" pageNumber="452">
Figs. 
<number box="[892,916,1571,1592]" pageId="13" pageNumber="452" value="10.0">10</number>
</figureCitation>
C– 
<number box="[946,970,1571,1592]" pageId="13" pageNumber="452" value="10.0">10</number>
