<figureCitation captionStart="FIGURE 8" captionStartId="10.[151,250,1661,1683]" captionTargetBox="[222,1371,366,1643]" captionTargetId="figure@10.[203,1384,349,1655]" captionTargetPageId="10" captionText="FIGURE 8. Male genitalia of Merodon neonanus sp. n. A – B. epandrium, lateral view; C. hypandrium, lateral view; D. distal end of aedeagus, ventral view; A—Greece; B—FRY of Macedonia; ab—aedeagal box; n—notch on theca to which is attached the aedeagal apodeme; ih—inner processes of the hypandrium." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/245535/files/figure.png" pageId="13" pageNumber="452">
